# MindVault – Personal Knowledge Management App

Build a premium, offline-first PKM web application using HTML5, CSS3, and Vanilla JS (ES6 modules). No frameworks.

## Proposed Changes

### CSS Foundation

#### [NEW] [variables.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/variables.css)
Color palette, typography, spacing, radius, shadows, z-index, transitions as CSS custom properties. Theme support (dark/light) via `data-theme`.

#### [NEW] [reset.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/reset.css)
Modern CSS reset.

#### [NEW] [layout.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/layout.css)
App shell: sidebar, navbar, main content area, grid layouts, page transitions.

#### [NEW] [components.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/components.css)
Cards, buttons, inputs, modals, toasts, tags, badges, editor toolbar, calendar grid, heatmap, mood selector, skeletons.

#### [NEW] [animations.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/animations.css)
Keyframes: fade-in, slide-in, ripple, skeleton shimmer, toast slide.

#### [NEW] [responsive.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/responsive.css)
Breakpoints for tablet (≤1024px) and mobile (≤768px). Sidebar collapse, FAB, stacked layouts.

#### [NEW] [style.css](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/css/style.css)
Master import of all CSS files.

---

### Core JS Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [storage.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/storage.js)
Abstract StorageManager class wrapping LocalStorage. CRUD for entries, notes, categories, tags, settings. Supabase-swappable interface.

#### [NEW] [utils.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/utils.js)
Date formatting, ID generation, debounce, word count, reading time, DOM helpers.

#### [NEW] [router.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/router.js)
Hash-based SPA router. Registers page render functions, shows/hides page sections.

#### [NEW] [ui.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/ui.js)
Toast notifications, confirm modals, loading skeletons, ripple effects, sidebar toggle.

#### [NEW] [app.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/app.js)
Bootstrap: init storage, register routes, bind global events, render initial page.

---

### Features

#### [NEW] [editor.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/editor.js)
ContentEditable-based rich text editor. Toolbar: bold, italic, underline, strikethrough, highlight, code, blockquote, lists, checklist, links, undo/redo. Markdown shortcuts.

#### [NEW] [journal.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/journal.js)
Journal page: auto-create today's entry, mood selector, category/tag pickers, autosave, word count, favorite/pin, archive/trash.

#### [NEW] [notes.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/notes.js)
Notes page: masonry/grid of note cards, color labels, CRUD, duplicate, move category, archive/trash.

#### [NEW] [dashboard.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/dashboard.js)
Dashboard: greeting, date, streak cards, recent entries, pinned/favorite itemsrnal, writing stats, calendar mini-preview, quote placeholder.

#### [NEW] [calendar.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/calendar.js)
Monthly calendar grid with entry indicators. Navigate months/years. Click date → open journal.

#### [NEW] [search.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/search.js)
Global search across entries & notes. Live search, result highlighting, search history.

#### [NEW] [filters.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/filters.js)
Filter system: date ranges, mood, category, tags, favorites, pinned, archived, trash.

#### [NEW] [analytics.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/analytics.js)
Stats cards, streak tracker, GitHub-style heatmap (canvas), tag/category bar charts, weekday activity.

#### [NEW] [settings.js](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/assets/js/settings.js)
Theme toggle, accent color picker, font size, autosave toggle, export/import JSON, reset data.

---

### HTML

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///d:/code/Journal%20Planner/index.html)
Single-page app shell. Sidebar nav, top navbar, page sections (dashboard, journal, notes, calendar, search, analytics, settings). ES6 module script entry point.

## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing
- Open `index.html` via local dev server and visually verify:
  1. Sidebar navigation switches pages correctly
  2. Dashboard shows greeting, stats cards, recent entries
  3. Journal creates today's entry, editor toolbar works (bold, italic, lists)
  4. Notes can be created, colored, pinned
  5. Calendar renders current month, clicking dates works
  6. Search returns results with highlighting
  7. Analytics shows stats and heatmap
  8. Settings theme toggle switches dark/light
  9. Responsive: resize to mobile width — sidebar collapses, FAB appears
  10. Data persists after page reload (LocalStorage)
